oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Knights of Columbus Medal
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Medals
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: George Fossick, a student at Christian Brothers College from 1883-1886, became a member of the Knights of Columbus. This medal belonged to him.
